<topic id='supporting_definition_organisation_data_service.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Supporting Information: Organisation Data Service - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_data_service">Organisation Data Service</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_data_service">ODS</xref>) is provided by 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 is responsible for the day-to-day operation of the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_data_service">Organisation Data Service</xref>
 and for its overall development.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_data_service">Organisation Data Service</xref>
 is responsible for:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                     keyref="supporting_definition_health_and_social_care_organisation_reference_data">Health and Social Care Organisation Reference Data</xref>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>Reference data for healthcare practitioners and</p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>A range of associated data and supporting products.</p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 is responsible for the day-to-day operation of the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_data_service">Organisation Data Service</xref>
 and for its overall development.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_data_service">Organisation Data Service</xref>
 provides:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
Central allocation of new or revised 
                                <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_organisation_identifier">ORGANISATION IDENTIFIERS</xref>
 and 
                                <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_organisation_site_identifier">ORGANISATION SITE IDENTIFIERS</xref>.                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>Help, advice and query resolution on the content and use of the national reference data</p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>Development of the Information Standards in this area</p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>Further development of the range of national reference data.</p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
For further information on the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_data_service">Organisation Data Service</xref>, see the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_data_service">Organisation Data Service</xref>
 pages of the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 website at: 
              <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/organisation-data-service"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Organisation Data Service</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
For enquiries, email the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_data_service">Organisation Data Service</xref>
 Helpdesk at: 
              <xref href="mailto:exeter.helpdesk@nhs.net"
               scope="external"
               format="html">exeter.helpdesk@nhs.net</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
</body>
